examples.en: Don't try to palliate your constant lying by claiming that everybody lies.
I'm only claiming what is rightfully mine.
The number claiming dole went up by 3,500.
Don't be taken in by products claiming to help you lose weight in a week.
It came to my attention that Jenny was claiming overtime pay for hours she had not worked.
She knew he was a liar when he started claiming that he was an astronaut.
A letter appeared in The Times claiming Fleming as the discoverer of penicillin.
The homeowner is claiming that local firefighters were dilatory in responding to the call.
Their landlord regularly milks them for extra money by claiming for damage to his property.
The company is claiming that there will be huge financial rewards for enterprising sales representatives.
